8.16.20  1:51 am   Do you write your script and music at the same time?

     anything sung, is written during the writing process. this includes the exact chord arrangement of any parts in a video that are sung. Everything else, the underscoring, is done entirely after everything else has been recorded and also after the graphics are done

     It seems so perfect together.

     the score is done very carefully to fit with everything. the score is the secret weapon that hypnotizes you into thinking anything i say is good

     Same with your songs, do you write the lyrics and music at the same time?

      yes
